2 ACTS OF THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY
(2) Every qualified person who vaccinates his or her own dog shall comply with the vaccination certificate and
tag requirement provisions of subsection (1) of this section and the administrative regulations promulgated
under KRS 258.075.
(3) Every owner of a cat or ferret shall show proof of a valid rabies vaccination upon request of an animal control
officer or peace officer.
Signed by Governor April 13, 2026.

